@chapter Quickstart

Most important keys:
@table @kbd
@item C-g
	Cancel the current operation
@item C-s
	Save(as) file. Identical to @code{M-x save-spreadsheet}, and similar to @code{C-x C-c}
@item C-x C-c
	Exit @code{neoleo}
@end table

Other highly useful keys:
@table @kbd
@item C-c
	Copy cell formula to clipboard
@item C-l
	Set alignment of current cell left
@item C-r
	Set alignment of current cell right
@item C-v
	Paste formula in current clipboard to current cell
@end table

This is by no means a complete list of the key bindings. There are many more described in
the rest of this manual.
